Articles.Content: If Klunk Flod will release ' Dark side of the Mun'???? =P

The Munatic is on the pad

The Munatic is on the pad

Remembering engine models and daisy cutters and laughs

Got to keep the missiles on the path

The Munatic is in the pod

The Munatics are in my pod

The duct tape holds their green faces to the wall

And every day crashes kill them all

And if the boosters ignite many seconds too soon

And if there\'s no-one left to kill

And if your ship explodes with dark forbodings too

I\'ll see you on the dark side of the Mun

The Munatic is almost dead

The Munatic is almost dead

You press the button, you eat the muffin

You re-arrange me till I fly

You lock the door

and throw away the key

There\'s someone in my head and it\'s light green

And if the exhaust bursts thunder in your ear

You scream and no-one seems to hear

And if the team your in starts yelling loud at you

I\'ll see you on the dark side of the Mun

\'I see ya on the dark side of the Mun!\', as inscribed on some old tire

P.S. iamwearingpants, that\'s a nice one
